<font color="red">'96</font></h2>
<b><font color="red">The Candidate's Briefing Book</font><p>

<i>Edited by Stuart M. Butler <br>
and<br>
 Kim R. Holmes</i>
<p><a href="/heritage">The Heritage Foundation</a><br></b>
