<DOCOLDNO>IA024-000249-B038-225</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.sbsc.org:80/nationalreview/extra/082896x.html 204.71.237.86 19970108093918 text/html 13680
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 09:39:35 GMT
Last-modified: Wednesday, 04-Sep-96 22:31:45 GMT
