<p>

<li>Elaine Dutka, <I>op. cit.</I>

<p>

<li>Jack Cheevers. &quot;Censorship Fears Raised After GOP Criticism.&quot;
<I>Los Angeles Times</I>. 7 June 1995:B-1.

<p>

<li>Elaine Dutka, <I>op. cit.</I>

<p>

