<a href="bg1086c13.gif">Chart 13</a>: 1.81 Percent Average Annual Growth Since Reagan Left Office<br>
<a href="bg1086c14.gif">Chart 14</a>: Lower and Middle Income Families Suffer Most During High Tax Era
</td></tr></table>
</center><p>




<b>Endnotes:</b>
<P><ol>
