<p><li>
    <i>Ibid.</i>, pp. B10-B17. Similar findings are reported for small businesses generally in a survey conducted by the Center for the Study of Taxation, a public policy organization focused on estate tax reform. See <i>Federal Estate and Gift Taxes: Are They Worth the Cost?,</i> Center for the Study of Taxation, 1996, pp. 9-11.
<p><li>
